    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've heard about some bad stuff with antibiotics and statins like muscle damage or whatever. but u said they're \"often managed.\" does that mean they dont actually clash? if i just take the simvastatin in the morning and the clarithromycin at night, would that fix the problem so i can just start my meds now without going to urgent care?",
